%F A381483 a(n) = A000108(n)*(A000108(n) + 1)*(2*A000108(n) + 1).
%e A381483 For n=2, the short leg is A382608(2,1) = 3 and the long leg is A382608(2,2) = 4 so the area is then a(2) = (3 * 4 )/2 = 6.
